data.title: ENGLISH CLASSES
data.text:
We’re a Christ-centered community teaching English language skills. Our goal is to engage students intellectually, emotionally, and spiritually, and give them opportunities to better communicate and participate in society.

Tuesdays, 7-9pm | September-May | Faith Church

FIEC teaches all levels of English, from those who don’t know English at all to those who simply need help with pronunciation or workplace language skills.

FIEC Kids

Students’ children (ages 6 weeks-13 years) are invited to FIEC Kids, where preschool and early elementary children play and have a lesson, and older children get help with homework, play games, and work on literacy. Use the buttons below to learn more!
